{"tid":944591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美貌炸裂！越南女團主唱　清純臉蛋小蠻腰吸粉絲","createTime":"2018-12-17T09:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T08:20:33.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec3827fbb384fd58cc48f409283bad6daebbf07","tid":944591,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"偶像女團可不是日韓才有，越南女團LIME的性感程度也超級爆表！其中主唱Liz洋娃娃一般的美貌堪稱「臉蛋天才」，為她吸引了國內外一大票死忠粉絲。<br />\n<br />\nLIME在2015年出道，曲風甜美可愛，曾赴韓國發展培訓，也上過韓國綜藝節目。成員有Emma、Liz和負責饒舌部分的Ivone。<br />\n<br />\n1993年出生的主唱Liz有一雙大眼睛，皮膚超白皙，長得超像洋娃娃，偶爾會在社交網站曬出泳裝照，臉書帳號是「Phan Kim Cương」，原來她的身材也超火辣的。據悉，她從小就喜歡唱歌，參加過越南許多選秀節目，還曾贏得5億越南幣（約72.5萬元台幣）獎金呢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXCQDBN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXCQDBN.png&h=852f8dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APYTBot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPYTBot.png&h=a5255589&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da6f0b9ceda27e150775ff760353d97bc66c61c4","tid":944591,"uid":217158,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"咪又係整 咁同韓國個d女星有咩分別"},{"pid":"831b6ce82fd66bab34c92bcfc0560604140ff422","tid":944591,"uid":129148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/48144707_124122975276273_6826463617748041728_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=be74b9fc36773db678494c37858529a9&amp;oe=5C9BC751\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F48144707_124122975276273_6826463617748041728_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Dbe74b9fc36773db678494c37858529a9%26oe%3D5C9BC751&h=66e2accf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲PS裝甲好厚下喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b574bbd41c7caec8d52974df892a322654bac6c","tid":94459